_sText: This is a weird map. i made it because a friend and i like to play on normal maps against bots that only use knives. i figured i could make a fun map for us to do that on so here it is. 6 ct's and 20 t's. the t's are supposed to be bots. i guess they could be real players but i dont know how fun it would be. ct's have a buyzone and t's dont. thats pretty much it. have fun!
